biotools.summary: Collection of high-dimensional cytometry benchmark datasets in Bioconductor object formats | Data package containing high-dimensional cytometry data sets in SummarizedExperiment and flowSet formats | R code to reproduce example in Figure 1 in our HDCytoData paper | The HDCytoData package is an extensible resource containing a set of publicly available high-dimensional flow cytometry and mass cytometry (CyTOF) benchmark datasets, which have been formatted into SummarizedExperiment and flowSet Bioconductor object formats. The data objects are hosted on Bioconductor's ExperimentHub platform
